WEBVTT

00:06.844 --> 00:08.398
<i>Previously on</i>
Penny Dreadful...

00:08.832 --> 00:09.862
Do you believe me?

00:10.027 --> 00:11.615
What are you asking
me to believe?

00:11.640 --> 00:13.367
<i>That you were
hunted by vampires?</i>

00:13.429 --> 00:15.147
That you commune
with Satan?

00:15.172 --> 00:17.014
I've lost the immortal
part of myself.

00:17.039 --> 00:19.445
No matter how far you have
walked from God,

00:19.470 --> 00:21.411
He is still waiting ahead.

00:21.665 --> 00:23.219
Vanessa:
Where is your master?

00:23.410 --> 00:25.609
Soon you'll meet him again.

00:25.634 --> 00:26.219
Again?

00:26.370 --> 00:27.770
Don't you remember, my lady?

00:27.783 --> 00:28.929
When was this?

00:28.999 --> 00:30.742
In the white room.

00:30.767 --> 00:31.787
Why do you think
he was talking

00:31.812 --> 00:32.892
about the Banning Clinic?

00:32.917 --> 00:35.336
This has to be the room where
I met the Master in the past!

00:35.449 --> 00:36.590
I know what I'm asking.

00:36.630 --> 00:37.660
I don't think you do.

00:37.685 --> 00:40.344
<i>Hypnotism can be
extremely traumatic.</i>

00:40.387 --> 00:41.427
Are you alone?

00:41.452 --> 00:43.195
- Always.
- No one comes in?

00:43.220 --> 00:45.402
An orderly with the food.

00:52.885 --> 00:54.285
I've brought your food,
Miss Ives.

01:01.992 --> 01:05.203
♪

